docs.text: Welcome to python-interview python-interview are fun, interesting, and fun programming. I will make a world with you. python_interview python-interview 모듈. Please put in a description of the module. Examples: python-interview 사용법은 아래와 같습니다. $ pip install ./ $ python-interview-ping 추가적인 설명은 여기에! Attributes: Name Type Description nnn int 사용되지 않는 시범용 변수 Todo 무한한 모듈의 발전 꿈 꾸며! Dreaming of infinite module development! ping () Example function with PEP 484 type annotations. Returns: Type Description 리턴 없이 화면 print Source code in python_interview/python_interview.py def ping (): """Example function with PEP 484 type annotations. Returns: 리턴 없이 화면 print """ if len ( sys . argv ) > 1 : n = int ( sys . argv [ 1 ]) print ( f " { 'p' * n } ong" ) else : print ( 'pong' )
